WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
From the menu FLOWERS choose interesting category.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
This will be a "Congratulations" for us.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:17.000
We see all proposals for the composition of bouquets on two pages.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Select composition in individual taste.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.000
When you find an interesting product - click "MORE" button.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Now, we see an exact description of the product and a bigger photo.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Red Flower informs us that the price is final and there are no additional fees.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:42.000
You can also view the terms of deliverty to make sure that the flowers will be delivered on time.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.000
The next step is to choose the size of our bouquet.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:48.000
When you are sure of your choice, ADD TO BASKET.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:51.000
Open up your basket with a list of products.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.000
You can add many extras to order e.g. a special ticket, wine, chocolates or a vase.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:01.000
To add a vase click "Add other" and then choose the vase.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:07.000
Add Vase to your cart and automatically go back to our order.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.000
When you added all the interesting products you must accept terms and conditions of delivery and click "ORDER".

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Now we have to fill Recipient's details. Fields marked with an asterisk are required.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:22.000
The more data you enter, will be easier and faster for a courier.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:27.000
Give your phone number in case of problems. Additional information could be also very important.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.000
The next step is to enter the sender's details.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:41.000
The email address and phone number are also very important.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:52.000
By clicking next shows us a summary. This is the last moment to change your details.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:57.000
The final step is to select and make payment. Poczta Kwiatowa offers many opportunities for payment.

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:01.000
For electronic banking, you can see when your transfer will be realized.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:06.000
It was only after confirmation by the bank payment order may be executed.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:17.000
When you select a payment method - click "PAY".

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:20.000
The order was made. The resulting order number must appear in the title transfer.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.000
Clicking the "PAY" takes us to the selected bank, where we can make a payment.

